#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center><button>Done</button> button on anonymous submission</h2>
This button submits a new record for consideration by the local coordinator.
On successful completion, the window terminates.  This button will not be
visible on the printed sheet, and will be disabled until all the required
fields are filled in when it is actively taking user data.

